llow, she whispers.</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;”Hey. Thanks for that.”</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;”For what, the drink?”</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;”No, dummy. Keeping me from makin’ another mistake.”</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;”Don&#039;t mention it. You got me to go in there and apologize to Frankie, after all.”</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;”Awwww, you did? That&#039;s good. I just expected ya to choke out a fake compliment.”</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;”No, I didn&#039;t even have to do that. She actually looked nice.”</div></li><li class="li1"><div class="de1">&gt;”I knew she would; that&#039;s why I bought the shit. Now come on… I think we&#039;re gonna have to discuss that promotion a bit sooner than planned…”</div></li></ol>        </div>
