&gt;”How’d it go? You didn&#039;t rat me out, didja?”
&gt;”No, but-”
&gt;”But nothin’. I don&#039;t give a shit about the rest of the interview. So long as you didn&#039;t sing like a canary, I don&#039;t care.”
